tps://cdn.star.nesdis.noaa.gov/GOES16/ABI/SECTOR/sr/GEOCOLOR/600x600.jpg\" title=\"\" width=\"600\"/></a<a></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>National Weather Service </strong>— <a<a href=\"https://cdn.star.nesdis.noaa.gov/GOES16/ABI/SECTOR/sr/GEOCOLOR/600x600.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Infrared Satellite image</strong></a<a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"https://www.star.nesdis.noaa.gov/GOES/sector.php?sat=G16&amp;sector=sr|\">Follow this link for additional infrared views &gt;</a></em></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2664369\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2664369\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Regional Radar Image</h2>\n<p align=\"CENTER\"><a alt=\"National Weather Service radar image showing portions of central and northern Arizona\" href=\"https://radar.weather.gov/ridge/standard/SOUTHROCKIES_0.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><img align=\"BOTTOM\" border=\"2\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://radar.weather.gov/ridge/standard/SOUTHROCKIES_0.gif\" title=\"\"/></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://radar.weather.gov/?settings=v1_#/\" id=\"https://radar.weather.gov/?settings=v1_#/|\">Follow this link to view a more detailed radar map &gt;</a></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2664365\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2664365\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Today's Weather Story</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.weather.gov/fgz/\" target=\"_blank\"><img align=\"BOTTOM\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://www.weather.gov/images/fgz/WxStory/WeatherStory2.png\" title=\"\" width=\"640\"/></a><br/>\n<em>If the date is not today's <a href=\"https://www.weather.gov/fgz/\" id=\"https://www.weather.gov/fgz/|\">click here to view additional Weather Stories </a></em></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6741880\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6741880\">\n<div id=\"weather-40A7B121-DFCD-4060-1D591A6111F079C1\">\n<p class=\"loadingMsg\">Loading weather forecast...</p>\n<!-- begin Weather widget-->\n<div class=\"WeatherWidget\" data-latlng=\"36.059117257442715,-112.10929870605469\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<figure class=\"-left w-weather-icon\" style=\"width:200px; margin-bottom:30px; display:none;\">\n<img alt=\"National Weather Service Icon\" src=\"https://www.weather.gov/error_nws/nws_logo.gif\" title=\"National Weather Service Icon\"/>\n</figure>\n<h2>Grand Canyon Village Weather Forecast</h2>\n<div class=\"w-alerts mb-5\">\n<h3 class=\"text-danger\">Hazardous Weather Conditions</h3>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Weather Forecast -->\n<div class=\"Component\">\n<h3 class=\"Alerts-severity w-station\"></h3>\n<span>Lat: <strong class=\"w-lat\">36.059117257442715</strong> Long: <strong class=\"w-long\">-112.10929870605469</strong></span>\n<p class=\"w-updated-container\" style=\"display:none;\">Last updated: <span class=\"w-updated\"></span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-5\">\n<div class=\"card w-current-container\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div class=\"card-body\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<h4 class=\"card-title mb-3\">Current Conditions</h4>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 col-md-12 col-lg-4\">\n<img class=\"w-icon\" src=\"\" style=\"width: 100px; height: 100px; margin-right: 1em;\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-3 col-md-12 col-lg-3\">\n<p class=\"w-textdescription\"></p>\n<p class=\"myforecast-current-sm w-temperature-f\" style=\"font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:bold\"></p>\n<p class=\"myforecast-current-sm w-temperature-c\" style=\"font-size:1.125rem\"></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-5 col